      <title>汉堡王老板的销售额因餐厅业务下滑加剧而受损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/burger-king-owner-s-sales-hurt-by-deepening-restaurant-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Restaurant Brands International Inc. 第二季度的销售额增长低于预期，这是消费者情绪低落袭击餐饮业的最新迹象。]]></description>
