      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/european-gas-steadies-as-russian-transit-continues-amid-fighting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:41:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
